				Posted in <a href="https://venmurasu.in/category/%e0%ae%b5%e0%af%86%e0%ae%af%e0%af%8d%e0%ae%af%e0%af%8b%e0%ae%a9%e0%af%8d/" rel="category tag">வெய்யோன்</a> <span class="on-date"> on <a href="https://venmurasu.in/2016/02/24/%e0%ae%a8%e0%af%82%e0%ae%b2%e0%af%8d-%e0%ae%92%e0%ae%a9%e0%af%8d%e0%ae%aa%e0%ae%a4%e0%af%81-%e0%ae%b5%e0%af%86%e0%ae%af%e0%af%8d%e0%ae%af%e0%af%8b%e0%ae%a9%e0%af%8d-68/" rel="bookmark" title="12:00 முப"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2016-02-24T00:00:35+05:30">பிப்ரவரி 24, 2016</time></a></span><span class="by-author"> by <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="https://venmurasu.in/author/mahasrinivasan/" rel="author" title="SS எழுதிய எல்லா இடுகைகளையும் பார்க்கவும்">SS</a></span></span>.
				
